PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of ANNE CARRIER, of Quebec, Quebec, as a part-time director of the board of directors of the Port of Quebec Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of eight months, in the place of Margo Brousseau, whose term has expired.
